thread.title: Nancy
thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Nancy

author: Nancy
title: Nancy
text: I studied gallery art/photo in college. The American Frame quality equals the same excellent quality high-end gallery framing I previously used. However, and it's a BIG however, the S/H is entirely too expensive. Yes, quality frames require careful packing, but I've spent much less online for equal framing. American Frame will be my second choice in purchasing quality frames. If American Frame ever reduces their S/H fees, they will be my first choice.
